          <li>Responsible for the game itself or its development</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For official information, please visit the <a href="/official/" class="link link-primary">official channels</a>.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2>2. Intellectual Property</h2>
        
